<subSubSection id="15DE5FE0FF9EEF5DFF12F9CBFD80F958" pageId="54" pageNumber="55" type="description">
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF9EEF5DFF12F9CBFD80F958" blockId="54.[151,1437,1662,1760]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">
The tribe is endemic to the Neotropical Region, presenting 183 species belonging to 36 genera. Sixteen species, distributed in eight genera, are currently recorded for 
<collectingCountry id="25D34CFBFF9EEF5DFD69F917FC81F904" box="[748,820,1698,1724]" name="Brazil" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. Here we report for the first time the occurrence of species of this tribe for the 
<collectingRegion id="9F00C289FF9EEF5DFE26F973FD87F958" box="[419,562,1734,1760]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">Paraná State</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
